nodes.text: A male individual served as an agent in the Galactic Empire during the Imperial Era. For some time the agent met with Bokk Naarg, a Sullustan male who was attempting to defect from the partisans and who also claimed to have information on where the remaining partisans were receiving their information from. After the agents job was done and arranged for Naarg to be extracted, ISB Admiral Garrick Versio sent Inferno Squad to recover Naarg from the Singularity on Tellik Four Station.
